[[File:Simple.png|25px]] <span id="simple">'''Simple'''</span> is a very straightforward difficulty that is located in [[:Category:Class 2|Bottom Class 2]]. Most players will have almost no trouble travelling through this difficulty. It is located between {{Class1Difficulties|Effortless|25px}} [[w:c:jtoh:Effortless|Effortless]] (or [[File:Playgrounddif.png|25px|link=Playground]] [[Playground]]) and {{Class1Difficulties|Easy|25px}} [[w:c:jtoh:Easy|Easy]]. This difficulty is the final sub difficulty of Effortless as well. Since it takes up about the '''high''' spectrum of its parent difficulty, it is recommend to do beginner towers in other EToH fan games as many are around this difficulty.                        
