[[File:Simple.png|25px]] <span id="simple">'''Simple'''</span>s icon is, well, simple. All there really is here is a 2x2 checkerboard pattern. The top right corner and bottom left corners are a bright shade of green, while the other two corners are a darker shade of green.
==Obstacles==
As this is a sub-difficulty of an already simple difficulty, there will not be a spectrum.
*4.5 stud jump (C)
*4.3 stud jump (UC)
*0.975 stud wraparound (C)
*0.925 stud wraparound (UC)

